{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"30fd3fd5b3","title":"为谢子长烈士题词及碑文","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0d4c7d357d","index":0,"year":1939,"month":8,"day":23,"articleId":"30fd3fd5b3"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji13","name":"毛泽东全集第13卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji13.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji13":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1a983cc739","type":"paragraph","text":"为谢子长烈士题词及碑文","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"30fd3fd5b3"},{"id":"429670edb1","type":"paragraph","text":"（1939年8月23日）民族英雄，虽死犹生。民族英雄谢子长同志之基。谢子长，名德元，安定人，一九二五年在北平加入共产党，自此即以共产主义为解放中国人民之道路，创农民运动讲习班，组农协会，领导人民参加反帝反军阀运动，人民因有谢青天之称。一九二七年大革命失败后，子长起义于清洞，继参加渭南暴动，败不丧志，奔走西北华北各地，九一八事变后于陵甘之间组织反帝同盟军，后改为中国工农红军陕甘游击队，即是红二十六军之前身。一九三三年赴察哈尔参加抗日同盟军，失败后回陕北组织第二十七军，协同刘志丹诺同志建造了陵甘宁边区。一九三四年于河口之役负伤，一九三五年春因伤进世，竞政军民各界感子长之功德，改安定县为子长县，以志纪念。于政府及人民为子长立差之时书以叙之","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"30fd3fd5b3"},{"id":"f4b7625a40","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"30fd3fd5b3"},{"id":"f6c3ba8379","type":"paragraph","text":"中华民国二十八年七月初九日[1]谢子长（1897-1935），陕西省安定县（今子长县）枣树坪人。肤北红军和苏区创建人，中国工农红军态出指挥员：1935年2月21日，谢子长因伤重与世长辞，时年38岁。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"30fd3fd5b3"},{"id":"6685e18b1d","type":"paragraph","text":"谢子辰丽差民","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"30fd3fd5b3"},{"id":"a5f1be4597","type":"paragraph","text":"饭","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"30fd3fd5b3"},{"id":"668daa2252","type":"paragraph","text":"东装学意年年菜V","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"30fd3fd5b3"},{"id":"ce33ea731e","type":"paragraph","text":"风","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"30fd3fd5b3"},{"id":"b8d484903f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东为谢子长烈士的题词。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"30fd3fd5b3"}],"page":{"id":"deaa66e34d","publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"30fd3fd5b3","start":507,"end":508}}}},"__N_SSG":true}